summary: This is an email from October 9, 2021, forwarding attachments related to a Palm Beach Police Department trash pull and property receipt records. The email indicates these documents were received on October 8, 2021.

events.title: Receipt of PBPD Records
events.description: Records from the Palm Beach Police Department, including a trash pull and property receipt, were received.

events.title: PBPD Trash Pull
events.description: A trash pull was conducted by the Palm Beach Police Department, as referenced in an attached document.

keyFacts: The email forwards documents from the Palm Beach Police Department (PBPD).
The attachments include a property receipt dated October 8, 2021, and a trash pull report from November 6, 2006.
The email was sent on October 9, 2021, indicating ongoing document collection or review related to the Epstein case.
